    "long_instructions": "## Tell an Expository Data Story with AI\r\n\r\nUse AI Chat to analyze the Spotify data cards and tell an expository data story.\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\nDo This:\r\n1. Upload the **PDF file** of the Spotify data cards from the library.\r\n2. Ask AI Chat these questions:\r\n   - *Here’s a music streaming dataset. Help me write an expository data story based on this data.*\r\n   - *What kind of character might have a Spotify Wrapped that looks like this: [insert attributes]?*",
